title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 05 2015 Thu.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 05 2015 Thu (03:16:42)


On Today's Show:

RON BENNINGTON, TOM PAPA, ELVIS COSTELLO, ROB DUKES.

Ron Bennington is with Opie and Jimmy. They talk about music and movies. Tom Papa joins them as they talk about subliminal stuff in movies and logos.

They talk about Quentin Tarantino vs the police and take calls about it. They check out Jenny Hutt on Periscope.

Elvis Costello joins them and they talk about his new book and his career and life.

Rob Dukes of Exodus joins them and they talk about his friend DMC (of Run-DMC), Otto and George, and cars. They play his new song to end the show
